data.description: What a Great Home! This home was made for entertaining a large family, The backyard with Resort styled Tiki Hut/Beach Bar, an outdoor shower, a Jacuzzi, a bathroom, and areas for entertaining and eating were made to be used and enjoyed by all. Come home to this West Bradenton 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home! Lots to love about this home, it just goes on and on. Perfect for those outdoor gatherings. Newer A/C, New Solar Panels on the roof, New Water filtration system, NO HOA so bring your boat or Rv and live the Florida lifestyle. This home was made for living in… come see it today, you will love it..
